description: Supports spells, or attacks that use bows or wands. Instead of using that skill, you will throw a mine that will use the skill for you when you detonate it. Mines cannot use channelling skills.

mods.text: Supported Skills have % increased Mine Throwing Speed
Supported Skills have % reduced Enemy Stun Threshold
Supported Skills have +% to Critical Strike Multiplier

mods: Each Mine from Supported Skills applies 2% chance to deal Double Damage to Hits against Enemies near it, up to a maximum of 100%
Supported Skills have a Base Mine Detonation Time of 0.25 seconds
Supported Attack Skills cannot be used with Melee Weapons

mtx.description: Your Blastchain Mine Support or High-Impact Mine Support becomes a Void Emperor Effect.
mtx.name: Void Emperor Blastchain Mine Effect

name: High-Impact Mine Support
